column5: Hey, I'm not new to fishing, but I am certainly not all that knowledgable.  Is anyone interested in fishing with a noob? I'm out for all the knowledge and interest I can get. I have a lot of gear, but no boat.  Um, if anyone is interested, PM me, and we can exchange info and the like!
Welcome Brad, if you ever want to do some fishing on the Grand river here in Brantford let me know!
Hey Brad come on out and fish with us carp guys. How about Peir 8 tomorrow?
I would love to. I'm busy Friday, until late at night, and I work Saturday until evening.
Hopefully we'll fish together another time. If you see me say hello.
Well, if you look like your profile pic, I'll definetly notice ya, lol
